title: Week 6 Rankings 2022
description:
Field Yates, Stephania Bell and Daniel Dopp talk injuries, what players are climbing our rankings and some bye week fill-in options. Plus, Liz Loza joins to discuss some players she is higher on than consensus and answer your social questions including if she would rather have Breece Hall or Josh Jacobs for the rest of the season.
